The '''Gaora TV Championship''' is a [[professional wrestling]] [[Professional wrestling championship#Gimmick/style championships|championship]] owned by the [[All Japan Pro Wrestling]] (AJPW) [[professional wrestling promotion|promotion]]. On August 28, 2012, AJPW and Gaora TV announced that AJPW would introduce a new championship called the Gaora TV Championship. A tournament for the title took place from September 8 to October 7.

